  "texts": [
    "ASI is considered the next phase of technological progress after the formulation of a General form of AI, or Artificial General Intelligence (AGI).",
    "While AGI reaches the levels of human intelligence, ASI surpasses these levels, achieving supremacy over human intellectual abilities.",
    "Technically speaking, under the current approaches, the possibility of a Large Language Model achieving AI supremacy, or surpassing human intelligence, is rather an overshoot due to their modus operandi as we explained in the previous section.",
    "They were trained to predict the next word with high accuracy and predict patterns.",
    "Consequently, the aphorism that LLMs present even preliminary forms of an AGI seems to be scientifically unsound."
  ],
